{"id":3070,"date":"2025-05-17T10:58:42","date_gmt":"2025-05-17T03:58:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=3070"},"modified":"2025-11-25T08:36:29","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T01:36:29","slug":"dien-di-anh-sang-mun-san","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/dien-di-anh-sang-mun-san\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110i\u1ec7n di &#038; \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5n s\u1ea7n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, da d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 gom c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh l\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n chu\u1ea9n Y Khoa s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 y t\u1ebf chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n ra ngo\u00e0i.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111i\u1ec7n di l\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c m\u1ee5n v\u1edbi Sulfur 2.28%, Retinol 0.05%, Bakuchiol trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC Acne Care Ampoule TR v\u00e0o s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1i vi\u00eam sau n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng n\u1ec1n, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da sau n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 60 \u0111\u1ebfn 90 ph\u00fat<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng 05 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch nhau 07 &#8211; 10 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -4px; top: 343.007px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, da d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3621,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[59],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-3070","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-advanced-skincare-therapy","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/3070","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3070"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3621"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3070"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=3070"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=3070"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=3070"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated"